description: Corrected tables regarding sexually transmitted diseases: Tables 1 to 5 list the number of diagnoses of the five main sexually transmitted diseases, by age and health authority 2002-06. Table 6 lists the total number of new and other STI diagnoses by age and SHA 2002-06. Table 7 lists the number of chlamydia in the National Chlamydia Screening Programme diagnoses by age and PCT from 2003-04 to 2007-08. 24 p.
